Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:06.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以Love Live優勝為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:08.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們五人重新出發
