Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:17.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算入社大概也跟不上她們的練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:20.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只能繼續保持現在的五個人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正當我們這麼想時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我叫櫻小路希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一位堅強又拚命的新生出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:28.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:31.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們平常都像這樣聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也有很多零食喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我下次也帶章魚燒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,巧克力我吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:43.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂! 讓希奈奈先拿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別這麼死板嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#02 二年級與一年級)\N讓希奈奈先拿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓妳久等了 小希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家像這樣到齊之後就會開始練習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了Love Live嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像們夢想中的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那正是Love Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也會站上這裡…
