Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我並沒有在責怪小希奈子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該道歉的反而是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 給妳造成負擔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會再想想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其他一年級嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏rrrrr
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,日經平均全面下跌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可是預料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話這個月的目標會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Money…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的要我去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我有事想拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望妳去邀芽衣當學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:38.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個女生好像有話要跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這都是為了學園偶像社…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳 妳要不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:05.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要也來當學園偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米女同學要!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當學園偶像!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來妳喜歡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,米女同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:15.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請饒我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我現在也沒有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只能靠雙親的資助過活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,麵包的話我倒是有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,培根蛋麵麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我最近超愛吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我什麼都不會拿好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是四季跟妳說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的事 還叫妳邀我進學園偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳以後不用管她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有 大家都在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不准找我聊學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:52.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我對什麼學園偶像根本沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下一節是體育課 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:02.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來早上練過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:07.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,櫻小路同學? 櫻小路同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:14.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,櫻小路同學最近加入學園偶像社了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳早就累到不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誰叫妳突然就開始勉強自己晨練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:29.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像社果然很辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,並不是因為練習太嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是希奈子體能太差了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我早上也看到小希奈子在練跑耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是希奈子在自主訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽說妳昨天也是太陽都快下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還在屋頂上練習耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是希奈子在跟學姐們學習舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總覺得好像被誤解了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別在意那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們什麼都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我也不是很清楚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:14.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我試著調查了一年級的入社狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,似乎沒有學生打算加入學園偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要去管樂社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像社怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:24.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我這種人是跟不上她們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟她們的目標是優勝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐們真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(入社申請)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然都是堇害得根本沒人來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:45.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼又我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我想不到其他可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:49.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐們午安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 一年級有想入社的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我問過好幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但大家都婉拒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然都是堇害的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳很煩欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這大概是希奈子的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一定是因為希奈子加入的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說妳現在到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是都說是我的責任了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 要是我更有偶像光環的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 妳別在那邊亂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:28.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,班上有幾個同學看過希奈子練習的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在她們眼中 我好像練得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這並不是學姐們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:40.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一切都是不擅長運動的希奈子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要稍微練習慢慢適應就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 到時候再拉人就會太遲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:54.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不然把練習菜單改得簡單點?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得那樣是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說不定這樣做是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:07.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的確 我也非常想在Love Live拿下優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是 比起優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我更希望學園偶像能在這間學校紮根
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望大家能將母親起頭的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,共同編織描繪下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟是妳媽媽開始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:22.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們是否應該創造適合許多一年級加入的環境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:26.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,加以推廣本校的學園偶像活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼看 小香音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,實際上我們也必須有所改變才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我把練習菜單貼在這裡囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只練一個小時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣有辦法參加Love Live嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有意見的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就自己提一套做法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是妳不是沒拿下優勝就要回上海…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是堇該擔心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再來 為了招募更多一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(贈送章魚燒! welcome新社員!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吃章魚燒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像社正在屋頂練習
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請務必來觀摩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-也請參考一下我們新的練習菜單 -我們是學園偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論是誰都有辦法加入了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:30.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說是練習菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果這樣能讓有興趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,多少增加一些就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經不用練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還剩5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:22.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天就練到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟之前決定好的菜單一樣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還真是有點沒意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過好像還是滿累的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:43.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,練不夠的人就回家自己練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就來做伸展操
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不可以在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟這是大家一起決定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就這樣再多練一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:58.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我叫妳坐下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,麵包我已經吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在只能給妳這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:19.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不要 妳把我當成什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不可以太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這才是芽衣普通的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼會在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別在意我 跟她聊聊學園偶像的話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像的話題?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:37.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我 我又沒打算談那種話題…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,櫻小路妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:49.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有想過要試著當學園偶像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才入社了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道目標是優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也知道練習很嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是入社了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是…是這樣沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那妳就該繼續衝刺下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:09.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去試著相信自己想做 想當作目標的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,周遭的人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳都不該在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很好 再跑一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子果然還是認為該好好練習才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其實我也是 完全靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,連小希奈子也在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都只顧著自己練習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太狡猾囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒想到會在這種地方碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且還是同一個時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然還是改回去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:27.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然希奈子說這種話可能有點失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但希奈子果然還是想跟Liella!的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起為了優勝而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:40.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子所嚮往 當成榜樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:43.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是以優勝為目標拚命努力的學姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:48.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是不辭辛勞 積極努力的學姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:51.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也一直在想這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼做真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是把菜單改回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說不定就不會再有一年級加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子說不定就會變得孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算這樣 妳也願意繼續努力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:20.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,願意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,願意跟我們一起把優勝當成目標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,願意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一定能傳達給其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:38.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算辛苦 只要持續做著自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,未來一定能體會到更多樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家會想一起嘗試的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,應該也有辦法創造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會 我認為妳說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們就相信學園偶像的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:02.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的想法一定能傳達給她們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:03.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,差點就迷失目標了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還真的是疏忽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:12.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們太在意眼前的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們該努力的目標並沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:31.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們是Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就再跑一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,加油 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,澀谷香音…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:12.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方 總是能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名為希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:20.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在閃爍著 閃爍耀眼光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟會走向何處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場場相遇之中 雖然又會迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請試著去享受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,覺得「似乎能做到卻做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後做到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會很開心 想著要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整顆心都像是要跳了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情歡笑 放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續走向遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界廣闊無邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然也有景色會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但熱情會始終如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越許多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要彈奏出什麼樣的悸動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改變未來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:38.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 優勝候補
